<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_View_Helper_Navigation_Menu must be able to render attributes assigned to the assembly of the menu. Example:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
Menu_Home class extends Zend_Navigation
{
   public function __construct ()
   {
      $this-&gt;setPages(array(
         array (
            'id' =&gt; 'home',
            'label' =&gt; 'Home',
            'accesskey' =&gt; 'H'  /* new attribute */
         )
      );
    }
}
</code></pre>

